ZH: 这个地方被认为是圣地。
EN: This place is considered a holy site.

ZH: 我们计划去参观那个圣地。
EN: We plan to visit that holy site.

ZH: 在这个城市，每年都会举行圣地巡礼。
EN: In this city, a pilgrimage to the holy site is held every year.

ZH: 他们把这座山视为圣地。
EN: They consider this mountain a holy site.

ZH: 这个湖泊在当地被尊称为圣地。
EN: This lake is locally revered as a holy site.

ZH: 神圣的遗迹让这座城市成为圣地。
EN: The sacred relics make this city a holy site.

ZH: 他们告诉我们这将是一次来到圣地的经历。
EN: They told us this would be an experience of visiting the holy site.

ZH: 那个山峰被认为是心灵的圣地。
EN: That mountain peak is considered a sacred site for the soul.

